GetNRMRegionSearchData

GetNRMRegionSearchData?NRMRegion=Kangaroo%20Island

The Metadata - GetAdvancedListsData section shows how to retrieve the NRM names which can be used in this request.

Returns a list of a wells as a JSON array of objects - only two are shown below:

GetNRMRegionFromName

There is also the related query GetNRMRegionFromName?NAME=Kangaroo%20Island

The Boundary string which is returned is the geographical boundary in Google’s Encoded Polyline Algorithm Format. You can decode this into geographic coordinates using the polyline package.

Returns a JSON array of objects:
